648.0, 1179648.0)\n+ 26214.4 + 314,572.8\n= 2857369.5999999996\n\nmax( 6763315.2, 88064.0, 3170304.0, 3244032.0)\n+ 634060.8 + 314,572.8\n= 7711948.0\n\nmax( 1,258,291.2, 32768.0, 589,824, 294,912)\n+ 314,572.8 + 32768.0\n= 1,605,631\n\nmax( 3,381,657.6, 88064.0, 1,585,152, 473,344)\n+ 634060.8 + 314,572.8\n= 4,330,289\n\n\n\n实测\n\nTime：4.2511 ms\nCBI: 4307053\noutH = 2048:  2.98 ms\n\nDecoder: CBI = 44840\n\nTime: 9.6864 ms\nCBI: 9638396\noutH = 2048: 8.11 ms\n\nDecoder: CBI = 97921\n\nTime: 3.5757 ms (-23%)\nCBI: 3561813\noutH = 2048: 2.56 ms\nBLOCKK=512: 2.45 ms\n\ninPartitionK = 1024, 不折K\nTime：2.7416 ms\n\nDecoder:  CBI: 43216\n\nTime: 7.3642 ms (-34%)\nCBI: 7279958\noutH = 2048: 5.23 ms\nBLOCKK = 512: 4.66 ms\n\ninPartitionK = 1024，不折K\nTime: 6.2923 ms\n\nDecoder: CBI: 92595\n\n\n\n\n\n(51--60)(61--70) \n\nreport-176319.txt\n (31--40)(41–50)（inPartitionK = 512, 折K）\n\nreport-224337.txt\n (inPartiitonK=1024, 不折K）\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
